body.name: Mardi Gras Cloth Napkins Set of 6, Reusable Polyester Dinner Table Napkins for Family, Restaurant, Wedding, Party
features: REUSEABLE CLOTH NAPKINS - Our cloth napkins are made of polyester, which features on soft, smooth, lightweight, highly absorbent, stain resistant, reuseable, foldable and durable.

LARGE DINNER NAPKINS - Our oversized cloth napkins measures 20 x 20 Inch(50.5 x 50.5 cm), which can fit your dining table and placemats perfectly, also can be used as the hand towel for reducing the use of paper towels, an eco-friendly alternative to paper towels.

EASY CARE - Our Washable Table Napkins are easy to clean and can be hand or machine washed in cold water, air drying, do not bleach, warm iron if needed. The color is still the same after washing a few times, no fade after repeated use.

MULTI-PURPOSE - Our Cloth Napkins are a great way to make your dinning table welcoming, perfect for special occasions, such as family dining, festive dinners, wedding, birthday party or any other event, it will enhance the atmosphere at dinning. The cloth napkin set is a great gift for your family or friends as housewarming, birthday, Valentine's Day, St. Patrick's Day, Easter or other holiday gifts.

MONEY BACK GUARANTEE - We devote to provide the best customer service and bring the best shopping experience to every our customer. If you are not satisfied with our product, contact us and we can offer a full refund.
